* Carnage watched as Tankoor plodded past her, she would have thought that 
he would have detected her signature but she guessed that he was just 
playing dumb.
She slowly began to sneak up behind him but then noticed that Cyber Claw 
wasn't behind her. The clone must have decided to go along with her plan 
after all, no matter...it was up to her anyway.
Carnage snarled quietly as she came up right behind Tankoor, it was now or 
never!*

" Carnage, TRANSFORM!!!"

*Now transformed she stood in plain view of the Predacon drone, she put her 
hand on her hip and whistled to get his attention...*

" Hay! Pred Boy! Over here!"

* She snarled as she straightened up her posture, she crossed her arms and 
awaited for the seemingly dim witted drone to turn and see her.
It would be fun to fight again, especially when she didn't have an employer 
depending on the outcome.*
